  "title": "Product Design Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>In charge of providingengineering support for product modifications, cost reductions, manufacturing process improvementsResponsible f</li>\n  <li>In charge of leading and participating in design and development activities from concept to production with a well-defined Product Development Process.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in driving successful development of new product development projects, research and develop ideas for new and improved designs of the components part</li>\n  <li>In charge of generating design specifications, design proposals and/or product designs that meet customer requirements.</li>\n  <li>Responsible in working with cross-functional team involved in new product development and manufacturing</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Mechanical/ Manufacturing/ Electronics Engineering or related field</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of working expereince in product design in components</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
